{"s":"retractable-rollup-banner","img":"rollup-banner.jpg","badge":"Same-Day","cat":"Event Displays","name":"Retractable Roll-Up Banner","tag":"Professional retractable banners for church lobbies, stages, and events.","verse":"For God so loved the world that He gave His one and only Son","ref":"John 3:16","specs":[("Width","80cm or 85cm"),("Height","200cm"),("Frame","Aluminum — Economy & Luxury"),("Material","Polyester banner"),("Production","Same-day available")],"feats":["Pulls out and retracts in seconds","Economy and luxury aluminum stand options","Sermon series & scripture designs available","Same-day production on select orders","Includes protective carry bag"],"desc":["Retractable roll-up banners are the workhorses of church interior signage. Set one up in your lobby to welcome first-time visitors. Place two flanking the stage to frame your sermon series. Use them at registration tables for conferences or VBS.","The beauty of roll-up banners is their speed — pull up, lock in, done in under 30 seconds. They retract just as fast and stow in a slim carry bag, ideal for multi-use spaces and traveling ministries.","We offer 80cm and 85cm widths, both at 200cm height. Same-day production is available because we know Sunday does not wait."],"uc":[("🏛️","Church lobby welcome displays"),("🎤","Stage & pulpit flanking"),("📋","Registration & check-in tables"),("📅","Sermon series promotions"),("🎓","Conference & summit signage"),("🎄","Seasonal event displays")],"sizes":["80cm x 200cm","85cm x 200cm"]},
{"s":"stage-backdrop-banner","img":"backdrop.jpg","badge":"Event Fave","cat":"Event Displays","name":"Stage Backdrop Banner","tag":"Large-format fabric backdrops that transform your stage for any ministry event.","verse":"One thing I ask — to dwell in the house of the Lord all the days of my life","ref":"Psalm 27:4","specs":[("Material","Polyester Fabric"),("Frame","Aluminum alloy pop-up"),("Sizes","8x8 ft up to 10x20 ft"),("Print","Full-color, vibrant"),("Setup","Tool-free, under 5 minutes")],"feats":["Photo-perfect quality for video and photography","No wrinkles — fabric stretches taut over frame","Pop-up frame sets up in minutes without tools","Perfect for baptisms, weddings, holiday services","Sizes up to 10x20ft for large stages"],"desc":["A stage backdrop banner instantly elevates the look of any event. Whether hosting a baptism, Christmas production, wedding ceremony, or multi-day conference, the backdrop appears in every photo and video frame — it should look intentional.","Our backdrop banners are printed on smooth polyester fabric and mounted on an aluminum pop-up frame that sets up in minutes without tools. The fabric pulls taut to eliminate wrinkles, giving you a clean, professional surface.","Available from 8x8ft up to 10x20ft to fill any stage. Bring your custom design — sermon series artwork, church branding, scripture passages, or seasonal imagery — and we will print it in full color."],"uc":[("💧","Baptism ceremony backdrops"),("💒","Wedding & ceremony décor"),("🎄","Christmas & Easter productions"),("📸","Photo booth & media wall"),("🎤","Conference & summit staging"),("📺","Live stream backgrounds")],"sizes":["8x8 ft","8x10 ft","10x10 ft","10x15 ft","10x20 ft"]},
{"s":"ministry-canopy-tent","img":"canopy-tent.jpg","badge":"Popular","cat":"Event Displays","name":"Ministry Canopy Tent","tag":"Custom branded canopy tents for outdoor outreach, fairs, and community events.","verse":"The glory of the Lord filled the tabernacle","ref":"Exodus 40:34","specs":[("Sizes","10x10, 10x15, 10x20 ft"),("Frame","Heavy-duty aluminum alloy"),("Canopy","Polyester, full-color print"),("Setup","Tool-free pop-up"),("Includes","Carry bag + stakes")],"feats":["Print your church name & branding on all panels","Sturdy aluminum frame for outdoor conditions","Three size options for any event scale","Full-color printing on roof, valances, and sidewalls","Removable sidewalls for versatile configurations"],"desc":["A branded canopy tent is your ministry mobile billboard. Whether at a community fair, block party, farmers market, or public outreach event, your tent is the first thing people see — a fully branded tent tells them exactly who you are.","Our aluminum-framed canopy tents are built for repeated outdoor use. The pop-up frame sets up quickly and holds firm in typical outdoor conditions. The polyester canopy and optional sidewalls can be printed in full color.","Three sizes available — 10x10ft for small presences, up to 10x20ft giving you a full command post for larger events with room for tables, chairs, and ministry materials."],"uc":[("🏘️","Community fairs & festivals"),("🤝","Street outreach events"),("🌾","Farmers markets & expos"),("🏃","Sports & recreation events"),("🍽️","Church picnics & cookouts"),("📋","Charity drives & fundraisers")],"sizes":["10x10 ft","10x15 ft","10x20 ft"]},
{"s":"a-frame-popup-banner","img":"popup-banner.jpg","badge":"Portable","cat":"Event Displays","name":"A-Frame Pop-Up Banner","tag":"Portable pop-up banners for lobbies, tables, and event spaces.","verse":"Go into all the world and preach the gospel to all creation","ref":"Mark 16:15","specs":[("Shapes","Oval, Teardrop, Bean, Round"),("Frame","Fiberglass — lightweight"),("Banner","Polyester fabric"),("Print","Full-color"),("Assembly","Tool-free, under 60 seconds")],"feats":["Four shapes: oval, teardrop, bean-shaped, round","Lightweight fiberglass frame — easy to carry","Full-color printing in your church branding","Doubles as table display or freestanding banner","Assembles in under a minute without tools"],"desc":["A-Frame pop-up banners offer maximum visual impact with minimum setup time. Their unique curved shapes stand out from rectangular banners that crowd most event spaces, drawing the eye naturally.","Ideal for placing near tables at church events, flanking a registration desk, marking a welcoming area in your lobby, or guiding visitors at conferences. Lightweight fiberglass frame makes them easy to position anywhere.","Each banner comes with a carry bag for storage and transport — great for ministries that run regular events or outreach programs and need flexible, portable signage."],"uc":[("🏛️","Lobby welcome & wayfinding"),("📋","Registration & info tables"),("🎤","Speaker introductions"),("🎪","Event booth identification"),("🏫","Church school & classrooms"),("🌍","Conference & summit displays")],"sizes":["Small (2.8m)","Medium (3.4m)","Large (4m)","Custom"]},
